{"tid":581701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錢幣店失5張古董鈔 警放蛇拘休班警","createTime":"2018-03-05T14:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T15:25:28.000Z","uid":122,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5eaf5216b5704166a51be22aaf1ea976b14e62cd","tid":581701,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"旺角砵蘭街163-173號好旺角購物中心一家錢幣店，於上月26日下午疑被人偷去5張面值港幣50元的古董鈔票，53歲姓吳負責人其後發現有人在網上兜售該5張鈔票，遂於上周五向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報後派員假扮買家表示對這些鈔票有興趣，並相約賣家在旺角區見面，結果對方應約現身；其間警員拘捕涉案兩名分別35歲姓鍾和58歲姓黃的男子，經調查後，更發現鍾為休班警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n兩人涉嫌盜竊，已獲准保釋候查，須於4月中旬向警方報到。案件交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。警方強調，如任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180305/57908923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57908923&d=DiGK16OJczRZvohM6yohsARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=dffc690f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57908923&h=c0097bc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180305/57908923</a>"},{"pid":"c5a3af8d8c0a8d07bdee4a738e40d7420276d4aa","tid":581701,"uid":159821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b473f9f1e1a0553656e9662e544b22d61303df2","tid":581701,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"笑死仁"},{"pid":"23f51fb9b40a6169e7625f8dfc6d78689cc0e15d","tid":581701,"uid":45821,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:29:59.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母可唔可以叫佢地掛住個狗牌  大大隻字寫住 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">休班警</span></strong></span>  三隻字  等我地D蟻民可以避開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no